extendedInfo.description: If you are Young Jeezy's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Young Jeezy's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Young Jeezy's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Young Jeezy's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)************************Main Features ************************- Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics************************List of albums ************************- Let's Get It: Thug Motivation 101- The Inspiration- The Recession- Thug Motivation 103: Hustlerz Ambition************************List of lyrics ************************- .38- 3 A.M.- Air Forces- All We Do- Amazin'- And Then What- Ballin'- Bang- Bottom Of The Map- Bury Me A G- By The Way- Circulate- Crazy World- Done It- Don't Do It- Don't Get Caught- Don't You Know- Dreamin'- Everythang- Everything- F.A.M.E.- Gangsta Music- Get Allot- Get Ya Mind Right- Go Crazy- Go Getta- Higher Learning- Hustlaz Ambition- Hypnotize- I Do- I Do This- I Got Money- I Luv It- J.E.E.Z.Y.- Just Like That (What I Do)- Keep It Gangsta- Last Of A Dying Breed- Leave You Alone- Let's Get It / Sky's The Limit- Lose My Mind- Mr. 17.5- My Hood- My President- Never Be The Same- Nothing- OJ- Put On- Put On (Remix)- Showtime- Soul Survivor- Standing Ovation- Still On It- Streets On Lock- SupaFreak- Takin' It There- Talk To Em- Tear It Up- That's How Ya Feel- The Inspiration (Follow Me)- The Realist- The Recession (Intro)- This One's For You- Thug Motivation 101- Trap Or Die- Trapped- Trapstar- U Know What It Is- Vacation- Waiting- Way Too Gone- Welcome Back- What They Want- What You Talkin' Bout- Who Dat- Word Play
